Known limitations:
- Social PNG export is intentionally disabled for RC1 while the poster layout is redesigned.
- Only a small set of Major Arcana hero artwork assets has been validated; unfinished cards use symbolic fallback.
- Daily Energy uses local in-browser state only; there is no account system, saved history, backend, or analytics.
- The reading system is symbolic and behavioral, not deterministic fortune telling.
- Prompt copy relies on browser clipboard permissions.

